OL,3,CReading man pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,Cex-partner
OL,6,FA man has pleaded guilty to murdering
OL,7,Fhis ex-partner in Reading.
OL,9,FEdwine Kiplangat, 29, of London Road,
OL,10,FReading, admitted stabbing Linner
OL,11,FSang, 39, at an address on London Road
OL,12,Fin September 2025.
OL,14,FLinner died at the scene.
OL,16,FPolice say their relationship had
OL,17,Frecently ended- when Linner had
OL,18,Farranged to retrieve some property
OL,19,Ffrom the location.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
