CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779469557
OL,3,CReading man pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,Cex-partner
OL,6,FAfter knowing this, he planned to kill
OL,7,Fher and then escape.
OL,9,FKiplangat will be sentenced in July.
OL,11,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,12,FChief Inspector Stuart May, of the
OL,13,FThames Valley Police Major Crime Unit,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain firmly with
OL,15,FLinner's family at this incredibly
OL,16,Fdifficult time.
OL,18,F"Edwine and Linner had been in a
OL,19,Frelationship, and this had recently
OL,20,Fended. Linner had arranged to retrieve
OL,21,Fsome property from the location.
OL,26,@vD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
