OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779469557
OL,3,CReading man pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,Cex-partner
OL,6,F"The evidence shows that, knowing
OL,7,Fthis, Edwine had planned to kill her
OL,8,FHe did so and then sought to escape,
OL,9,Fshowing no regard for the injuries
OL,10,Finflicted on Linner.
OL,12,F"Let me be clear; domestic abuse has
OL,13,Fno place in our communities and we
OL,14,Fwill do everything we can to protect
OL,15,Fthose at risk and hold offenders like
OL,16,FEdwin Kiplangat to account.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
