OL,3,CReading man pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,Cex-partner
OL,6,F"This case demonstrates Thames Valley
OL,7,FPolice's commitment to investigating
OL,8,Fviolence against women and girls. If
OL,9,Fyou are a victim of violence then
OL,10,Fplease be reassured that we have
OL,11,Fspecially trained officers who will
OL,12,Flisten and support you.
OL,14,F"I would also like to encourage anyone
OL,15,Fwith concerns about a partner or
OL,16,Fexpartner to consider making a
OL,17,FClare's Law request.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
