OL,6,F"This allows people to ask police
OL,7,Fwhether a current or former partner
OL,8,Fhas a history of abusive behaviour. It
OL,9,Fis an important tool for helping
OL,10,Fpeople protect themselves and make
OL,11,Finformed decisions."
